ew ValueCodecProvider(),\n                new BsonValueCodecProvider(),\n                new MapCodecProvider());\n    }\n\n    public static final class ConstructorBackedMap extends LinkedHashMap<String, Object> {\n        public ConstructorBackedMap() {\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_WA2PjHqbaPbcEL3VqG9Z7JkI|fc_0253ad0729946a120169f53dc75408819db208afb083c04717", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.mongodb/bson/4.11.1/user-code-filter.json", "edits": [{"oldText": "    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"org_mongodb.bson.AbstractCollectionCodecTest**\"\n    }\n", "newText": "    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"org_mongodb.bson.AbstractCollectionCodecTest**\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"org_mongodb.bson.AbstractMapCodecTest**\"\n    }\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2293, "output": 916, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26761, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777679806816, "responseId": "resp_0253ad0729946a120169f53dbf483c819db6ca3da445364017"}}
